<prefix> = <ctrl>-<space>

# Windows
## Create new window
<prefix> c
## Navigate windows
<prefix> p
<prefix> n
<prefix> $WINDOW_NUM
## Close window
<prefix> &
# Rename window
<prefix> ,

# Panes
## Split horizontally
<prefix> "
## Split vertically
<prefix> %
## Navigate
<prefix> q
<prefix> hjkl
## Resizing panes
<prefix>+<arrow key>
## Move current pane left
<prefix> {
## Move current pane right
<prefix> }
## Zoom in on pane
<prefix> z
## Pane to window
<prefix> !
## Close Pane
<prefix> x

# Copying
## Enter copy mode
<prefix> [

# Session
## Create new session with name
tmux -s session-name
## Change session name
<prefix> $
## Show all sessions
<prefix> s
## Detatch from session
<prefix> d
## Kill session
tmux kill-session -t mysession

# Advanced
## Swap windows
:swap-window -s 2 -t 1


